name: Asymmetry USDaf Stablecoin
reason: USDaf is a CDP stablecoin built on Liquity v2 infrastructure by Asymmetry Finance, allowing users to borrow against their BTC and Yield-Bearing Stablecoins with user-set fixed interest rates for the first time. USDaf has been redeployed and is back better than ever, and we link to Cowswap for users to be able to acquire USDaf all across the Asymmetry website + dapp.
